subproject.description:
Project's main targets are:
1. Mine Action coordination capacity fully functional.
2. Mine Action coordination cost taken by state.
3. Military demining capacities sustained.
4. Humanitarian demining efforts connected with socio-economic component of mine action and funds for mine clearance maximized.
5. Project activities implemented in accordance to the project document and UNDP’s rules and procedures
subproject.title: Integrated Mine Action Program
